text: Raja Dr. Rudra Pratap Singh (Raja Jamo Estate) is an Indian politician. He belonged to Jamo kingdom of ancient UP. He was MLA from Gauriganj in 1962.He was elected to the Lok Sabha, the lower house of the Parliament of India from the Barabanki, Uttar Pradesh constituency of Uttar Pradesh as a member of the Indian National Congress. ==References== ==External links== * Official Biographical Sketch in Lok Sabha Website Category:Rajya Sabha members from Uttar Pradesh Category:Indian National Congress politicians Category:Lok Sabha members from Uttar Pradesh Category:5th Lok Sabha members Category:1936 births Category:Living people
title: Rudra Pratap Singh (politician)
